Stockholmsbörsen kring nollan – medicinteknikbolaget rasar efter vinstvarning
Stockholmsbörsen inledde onsdagens handel med en mindre uppgång. Bland medicinteknikbolagen rådde det skilda världar när Vitrolife rusar på rapport medan Raysearch rasar efter att ha vinstvarnat på tisdagskvällen. 
06 Nov 2019, 08:21 by Viktor Mölne

The Stockholm Stock Exchange around zero - the medical technology company collapses after a profit warning
The Stockholm Stock Exchange started trading on Wednesday with a slight increase. Among the medical technology companies, different worlds prevailed when Vitrolife rushed on report while Raysearch crashed after winning a warning on Tuesday night.
06 Nov 2019, 08:21 by Viktor Mölne
